12
00:00:34,070 --> 00:00:35,620
I have a favour to ask...

13
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:36,800
What is it?

14
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:41,640
Matsumoto has something he really wants to do.

15
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:43,030
Again?

16
00:00:43,040 --> 00:00:44,630
