17
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:45,230
Yes.

18
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:49,950
What does he want to do?

19
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:50,710
What is it?

20
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:55,820
He wants to set a world record in the high jump.

21
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:57,470
Huh?

22
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:58,750
Why?

23
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:02,360
I don't know, since he was crying...

24
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,310
Was he crying?

25
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:09,320
The current world record is 2m 45cm

26
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,780
2m 45cm? That's high.

27
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:14,110
