29
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:22,230
Wrong. That is why I'm dressed like this. Come on!

30
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:26,470
Don't make me explain everything. What does this outfit make me?

31
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:28,430
Kuroko (Stage assistant dressing in black).

32
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:32,430
He really wants to high-jump. What can we do?

33
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:34,110
Assistance, right?

34
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,710
Assistance?

35
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:38,590
Let's help him to high-jump, shall we?

36
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:41,510
Will he be satisfied?

37
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:44,270
Will he be satisfied, high-jumping with our assistance?

38
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:48,540
He will. He really wants to high jump.

39
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,870
Are you sure?

40
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,230
Will you help?

41
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,550
Yes. Yes, we will.

42
00:01:52,920 --> 00:02:00,480
Will he be able to exceed the world record of 2m 45cm set by Sotomayor from Cuba In 1993?

43
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:04,870
Wow, this is high.

44
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,390
Here he comes.

45
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:10,390
Good morning.

46
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,630
He's ready.

47
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:18,990
You may be thinking that

48
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:22,510
Matsumoto is being selfish again.

49
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,990
When you have been

50
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,350
in this field for a long time,

51
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,670
a time like this

52
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,190
