55
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,750
So it seems to be impossible

56
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,350
Yes.

57
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,870
So I hate to say this but

58
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,670
just a little is OK so

59
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,150
