Yes it is.

64
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,630
Is it that high?

65
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,230
I count on you guys.

66
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:05,950
Yes, we understand.

67
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,150
