74
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:18,950
Ready?

75
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,390
Yes

76
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:40,430
Hey hey hey. wait.

77
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,860
Timing was bad.

78
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,520
Timing was bad.

79
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:48,230
Not good at all.

80
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,230
Sorry.

81
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:53,910
You go there.

82
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:55,270
Yes, only timing.

83
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,550
Now, timing..

84
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,470
So it's just about timing then.

85
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:59,230
It's the timing, yes

86
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,510
Let's get off to the excellent start.

87
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:02,990
Ready?

88
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,670
Yes!

89
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,150
Three!

90
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:30,270
Matsumoto san!

91
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,270
Our fault?

92
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,990
Well, we tried our best!

93
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,910
What should we do?

94
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,230
We should go.

95
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,670
