102
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:58,720
Matsumoto

103
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:02,320
I think the angle was wrong.

104
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:06,480
I don't care that I couldn't.

105
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:11,230
The important thing is, everyone is going in the same direction. Right?

106
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:16,070
I'm not mad because I can't high jump.

107
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:19,900
If you're not going to try hard, just quit it!!

108
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,040
No, it's not that.

109
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,270
No, stop it.

110
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,990
Don't waste it.

111
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,510
You did a good job. Nice color.

112
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,950
Leave it to us.

113
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,230
It's angle.

114
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,350
Please come, we will be perfectly ready.

115
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,510
We'll be waiting.

116
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,350
Changing the mood, here's the 2nd challenge!

117
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,190
We should do a talk too.

118
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,150
Well

119
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:40,110
just let's do it, OK?

120
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:43,510
