Put it on there.

124
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,710
No no no..

125
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,630
What?

126
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,630
Sorry.

127
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,630
I thought it was angle.

128
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:25,470
Wasn't it strange?

129
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,270
No.

130
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:29,870
Let's try again. It's gonna be OK.

131
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:31,820
Sorry, but next time will be OK.

132
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,710
Sorry

133
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:34,070
Sorry

134
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,510
It'll be no problem at all.

135
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:38,550
Let him lay down.

136
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,150
It's OK.

137
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,230
So heavy!

138
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,110
Ouch!

139
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,550
Use your hands.

140
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,030
Take it off it hurts!

141
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:30,790
Lift him up!

142
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,790
Lift.

143
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,150
Matsumoto san!

144
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:52,150
Our image was once we lift him up, he will...

145
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:53,990
He would be pulled up high.

146
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,990
Then we could've thrown him over.

147
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:03,230
Go to Matsumoto's dressing room again to apologize

148
