Matsumoto is playing imaginary drums

149
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:17,110
I want to high jump!

150
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:24,310
Don't make me wear strange accessories.

151
00:08:25,530 --> 00:08:27,180
Too long.

152
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:31,850
