155
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,270
It's so high.

156
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,310
It is so high.

157
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,150
Let us begin!

158
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,830
We need one more. This side and that side.

159
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,070
Is it OK like this? This side is sticking out.

160
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,910
This is going to be good.

161
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:23,910
Right?

162
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:01,790
It was long.

163
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:06,470
