168
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,030
Yes.

169
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:24,710
Matsumoto is filling out an embarkation card

170
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,360
I am NOT an old man,

171
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:30,790
